Repository License Status
=========================

This repository does not currently declare a single project-wide license for
the original thesis code, documents, scripts, generated artifacts, or LaTeX
materials.

Third-party components keep their own upstream licenses and notices. The
current third-party inventory and provenance boundary is documented in
THIRD_PARTY_NOTICES.md.

Do not treat this file as permission to redistribute the original repository
contents under an open-source license. Before public release, submission
packaging, or redistribution outside the thesis review workflow, choose and
record an explicit repository license or supervisor-approved distribution
policy.
